data.title: Watch The Seven Deadly Sins
data.meta_description: When a kingdom is taken over by tyrants, the deposed princess begins a quest to find a disbanded group of evil knights to help take back her realm. Watch trailers & learn more.
data.text:
1. The Seven Deadly Sins

25m

A princess finds a former knight at a pub and joins a quest to reunite his group of cavaliers in order to overthrow tyrants and restore the kingdom.

2. The Sword of the Holy Knight

25m

When Gilthunder plants his sword in the center of the town and stops the village from making ale, only Meliodas can remove it, making him town savior.

3. The Sin in the Sleeping Forest

25m

Meliodas, Hawk and Elizabeth travel to the daunting Forest of White Dreams, where Meliodas goes to dangerous extremes to obtain information.

4. A Little Girl's Dream

25m

Diane joins the mission to free Ban from the Baste Dungeon, but the group is assailed by an enemy set on crushing the whole town and the Deadly Sins.

5. Even if You Should Die

25m

Golgius tries to seize the sword from Elizabeth and Meliodas; the sound of a mysterious bell drives the group to fight each other.

6. The Poem of Beginnings

25m

Elizabeth and Meliodas must fight Holy Knights Friesia and Ruin to proceed to the dungeon. An omen foretells of disaster on its way to Britannia.

7. A Touching Reunion

25m

Ban, Meliodas and company have finally reunited. Seeking a clue to the location of the Grizzly's Sin of Sloth, they head to the Capital of the Dead.

8. The Fearsome Pursuer

25m

King and Ban have a final showdown; Holy Knight Guila battles Meliodas, Diane and Elizabeth; Ban remembers Elaine and the Fountain of Youth.

9. Dark Pulse

25m

Elaine finally persuades King to rescue Meliodas and the others. Back in the capital, malcontent starts to stir among some of the Holy Knights.

10. The Vaizel Fighting Festival

25m

Upon learning the fighting festival's grand prize, Gideon, Meliodas, Ban and King decide to participate, as do Holy Knights Howzer and Griamore.

11. Pent-up Feelings

25m

In the final match of the festival's first round, Ban reflects on the first time he met Meliodas. Veronica and Griamore search for Elizabeth.

12. Bloodcurdling Canon

25m

During the last match of the festival, the venue breaks out in pandemonium when a group of Holy Knights attacks. What have they come for?

13. The Angel of Destruction

25m

Enclosed inside the Goddess Amber, Meliodas breaks free and reappears. Not his true self, he begins attacking his allies as well as his enemies.

14. A Reader of Books

25m

Meliodas and his pals begin a new search for the remaining Seven Deadly Sins. The Holy Knight Helbram dispatches assassins to crush the Armor Giant.

15. Unholy Knight

25m

Just as the attack overtakes the Armor Giant, Gowther appears, taking unexpected action. Elizabeth learns of Meliodas's past and the existence of Liz.

16. The Legends, Provoked

25m

Elizabeth's words convince Meliodas to fight, and it becomes clear who stole his consciousness. Hendrickson begins to resurrect the Demon Clan.

17. The First Sacrifice

25m

When Elizabeth is kidnapped, Meliodas, Ban and Gowther launch an attack on the capital. Meanwhile, King Arthur of Camelot confronts Hendrickson.

18. Even If It Costs Me My Life

25m

Diane has a brush with death while protecting Zeal. Howzer and Guila are forced into a struggle against formidable magical powers.

19. The Fairy King Waits In Vain

25m

King recalls how he met Diane 700 years ago and the sad event that occurred between him and Helbram. What promise did these once good friends make?

20. The Courage Charm

25m

In order to take Elizabeth back, Meliodas teams up with Arthur to fight a fierce battle against Hendrickson and Gilthunder.

21. The Looming Threat

25m

Merlin's appearance crushes Vivian's ambitions, and Meliodas is reunited with Elizabeth. Ban learns he must kill someone in order to resurrect Elaine.

22. What I Can Do For You

25m

Meliodas loses Elizabeth again. Ban confronts the person he must kill in order to save Elaine. Diane and company battle against the New Generation.

23. Despair Descends

25m

Pursued by the Seven Deadly Sins, Hendrickson makes two finds that give him the ultimate Demon power.

24. The Heroes

25m

Just when it seems as if the Seven Deadly Sins will be defeated by Hendrickson's overwhelming power, Elizabeth's power returns to her.

1. Revival of the Demon Clan

25m

As the kingdom begins to rebuild after the coup attempt, the king honors the Seven Deadly Sins for their bravery with a medal ceremony.

2. Existence & Proof

25m

With Fraudrin's manipulation of Hendrickson, the Ten Commandments return to the physical realm. King follows Ban to the Fairy King's Forest.

3. The Sacred Treasure Lostvayne

25m

Diane confronts Gowther after he manipulates Guila and Zeal's memories. With the return of the Demon Clan, new threats descend upon allied clans.

4. The Ten Commandments on the Move

25m

King struggles to fend off the giant Albion sent to destroy the Fairy King's Forest. Galand of the Ten Commandments appears before Meliodas.

5. Overwhelming Violence

25m

The fairies reconcile their differences with King as Ban leaves the forest. Meanwhile, Meliodas and gang are overwhelmed by the sheer power of Galand.

6. The Chief Holy Knight Atones For His Sins

25m

Hendrickson, thought to have been defeated in a battle against Meliodas, aids Gilthunder and the Holy Knights against a powerful Gray Demon.

7. Where Memories Lead

25m

An injured Diane awakens, having trouble remembering her comrades. With her memories fading, she heads for Megadoza, home of the Giant Clan.

8. The Druids' Holy Land

25m

Meliodas and others head to Megadozer in hopes of finding Diane. Meanwhile, a confused Diane encounters Galand of the Ten Commandments once again.

9. A Promise To A Loved One

25m

Acknowledging his lack of strength to face the Ten Commandments, Meliodas vigorously trains with the Druids of Istar to regain his sealed powers back.

10. What We Lacked

25m

Ban reflects on his past after returning to his childhood home in Ravens. Meliodas's allies train for their inevitable war with the Ten Commandments.

11. Father & Son

25m

A frail Zhivago reunites with Ban, his long-lost adopted son. Meanwhile, a wary King confronts Meliodas about his true intentions.

12. Where Love Is Found

25m

After a brief encounter with Meliodas, the Ten Commandments begin their attack on Britannia. A resurrected Elaine appears before Ban.

13. Farewell, Beloved Thief

25m

A revived but possessed Elaine attacks her lover, Ban, as Melascula and Galand of the Ten Commandments emerge to destroy those in their path.

14. Master of the Sun

25m

Jericho carries severely injured Ban and Elaine on her back while escaping from Galand and Melascula before stumbling into a bar deep inside a cave.

15. A Bloodcurdling Confession

25m

Gloxinia and Drole of the Ten Commandments lure strong fighters to Vaizel by offering to grant any wish to the winner of their Great Fight Festival.

16. Death-Trap Maze

25m

An elaborate trap-laden deadly maze constructed by Drole begins to weed out the weaker challengers that have gathered for the Great Fight Festival.

17. Legendary Figures

25m

The surviving challengers of the Great Fight Festival are split into pairs and made to face each other in a tag team battle.

18. For Whom Does That Light Shine?

25m

King and Diane continue their battle against opponents summoned by Gloxinia and Drole. Escanor refuses to fight against his fellow ally Gowther.

19. Meliodas vs.The Ten Commandments

25m

As Escanor's battle with Gowther comes to a dramatic end, Meliodas must now face the remaining Ten Commandments in an all-out battle.

20. Have Hope

25m

With Meliodas rendered powerless, Ban asks to be transported back so he can aid him in his fight against Estarossa and the other Ten Commandments.

21. Certain Warmth

25m

While caring for Meliodas, Elizabeth encounters a former Great Holy Knight thought to have perished long ago by the hands of Dreyfus and Hendrickson.

22. Return of the Sins

25m

With Ban and the Holy Knights paralyzed by Estarossa’s powers, Escanor shows up to thwart the fall of Liones at the hands of the Ten Commandments.

23. The Hero Rises!!

25m

As the situation inside Liones Castle becomes even more dire, Merlin, freed from Galand's Commandment of Truth, reappears in her former form.

24. So Long As You're Here

25m

Determined to kill his former leader for betraying their clan 3,000 years ago, Fraudrin takes on a newly resurrected darker, more powerful Meliodas.

1. The Light That Sweeps Away the Darkness

25m

Meliodas and Ban intercept a caravan transporting prisoners to the Ten Commandments, but demons still threaten villages in other parts of Britannia.

2. Memories of the Holy War

25m

King and Diane take refuge in the Fairy King's Forest to escape the Ten Commandments. But Gloxinia and Drole find them after a peaceful interlude.

3. Let There Be Light

25m

Looking like Gloxinia and Drole, King and Diane are transported back to Britannia 3,000 years ago. There they meet Meliodas, who's fighting for Stigma.

4. The Ten Commandments vs. The Archangels

24m

Led by Ludociel, the Four Archangels overwhelm the Ten Commandments. With no other choice, Derieri and Monspeet resort to extreme measures.

5. Emotional Maelstrom

24m

Elizabeth attempts to save Derieri and Monspeet from their Indura transformation. Defying Ludociel, Sariel and Tarmiel go to her aid.

6. We Call That Love

24m

The original Gowther comes to Diane and King with a request. King learns of a human revolt against Stigma and rushes to Gerheade's aid.

7. Deadly Sins,Unite!!

24m

King regains consciousness in the present, but Diane is still stuck in the past facing Zeldris. Drole watches calmly, but King is frantic with worry.

8. The Doll Seeks Love

24m

While King and the others search for him, the events that led Gowther to suppress his memories come to light. Then he meets Nadja.

9. The Cursed Lovers

24m

Diane tells Elizabeth that she met someone who looked just like her in the past. Meliodas denies knowing anything about it when Elizabeth asks.

10. The Life We Live

24m

On their way to liberate Camelot, Meliodas tells his comrades about the curse that two deities put upon him and Elizabeth 3,000 years ago.

11. The Hateful Cannot Rest

24m

The party heads to the city of Coland to dispel the distortion protecting Camelot. When Meliodas is trapped in darkness, they must fight without him.

12. Love is a Maiden’s Power

24m

Transformed into a giant snake, Melascula attacks Ban and the others. After Meliodas escapes the darkness, he unleashes his fearsome Assault Mode.

13. The Almighty vs. the Greatest Evil

24m

Meliodas regains the strength he had when he led the Ten Commandments. Escanor, whose power peaks at the stroke of noon, struggles against him.

14. A New Threat

24m

The Demon King orders Zeldris to capture Meliodas and kill the Deadly Sins. But when he calls upon the Ten Commandments, no one answers.

15. To Our Captain

24m

Chandler, Meliodas' former mentor, aids Zeldris. He infiltrates the Boar Hat to capture Meliodas, but the Deadly Sins stand in his way.

16. The Seven Deadly Sins End

24m

King prepares to face Chandler, who's returned in his demonic form. Gloxinia and Drole appear, risking their lives so the Deadly Sins can escape.

17. Our Choices

24m

Meliodas disbands the Deadly Sins and departs with Elizabeth. But his companions aren't going to let him go without a fight, and Hawk holds the key.

18. March of the Saints

24m

Merlin faces Zeldris, whom Meliodas has ordered to gather the Commandments. Margaret, Hendrickson and Dreyfus continue their search for Gilthunder.

19. The Holy War Pact

24m

Having taken over Margaret's body, Ludociel appears in Liones and declares a holy war against the Demon Clan. Chandler searches for Elizabeth.

20. Child of Hope

24m

In Camelot, Arthur searches for the Holy Sword Excalibur alone. Ludociel warns Escanor to give up his Grace of Sunshine, on pain of death.

21. Beginning of the Holy War

24m

Inside Camelot, Arthur makes his last stand against Meliodas and the others. Merlin comes to his rescue, but not before she falls under Cusack's spell.

22. War-torn Britannia

24m

The new Holy War commences as the allied forces of Stigma face off against the Demon Clan. Derieri decides to surrender her Commandment to Zeldris.

23. The One Twisted by Darkness

24m

Sensing Elizabeth's magic, Derieri appears before the Stigma army. Estarossa follows her, but Sariel and Tarmiel have other plans for him.

24. Rampaging Love

24m

Estarossa professes his love for Elizabeth. When he loses control after absorbing three of the Commandments, Stigma's army faces him in a final battle.

1. From Purgatory

25m

Ban searches purgatory for Meliodas. King, Deriri and the others head to Heaven's Theater to rescue Elizabeth, who's been abducted by Estarossa.

2. A Meeting with the Unknown

25m

Reunited once again, Ban and Meliodas prepare to face the Demon King, who they suspect holds the key to their escape from purgatory.

3. A Single-Minded Love

25m

With Wild now an ally, Meliodas brings Zeldris' tragic past to light as the newly formed trio make their way towards the Demon King.

4. The Victims of the Holy War

25m

Meliodas grapples with suddenly losing his memories of Estarossa. Zeldris, Chandler and Cusack threaten to overpower Merlin and the others.

5. The Tragic Strike

25m

Gowther reveals that his creator, the real Gowther, cast a forbidden spell on Mael and all those who knew him to end the Holy War 3,000 years ago.

6. Confront Despair!!

25m

Gowther takes on Mael to protect his friends. Diane also joins the battle, but the Archangel's power level continues to rise as he nears his final form.

7. Hope, Conflict, and Despair

25m

Mael changes form after absorbing four of the Commandments. King soon overwhelms him with his Spirit Spear, but Gowther tries to save the Archangel.

11. The One Who Stands Against a God

25m

Merlin's spell thwarts Meliodas' transformation. The Holy War seems to be over, but Elizabeth senses something is still terribly wrong.

12. We'll All Be Your Strength

25m

Escaping purgatory, Ban faces the Demon King, who now possesses Meliodas’ body. Elizabeth and the others make their way into the spirit world.

13. The End of a Long Journey

25m

Peace returns to the Kingdom of Liones. Although Elizabeth is still under a curse, Meliodas assures her there is a way to break it.

14. Farewell, Seven Deadly Sins

25m

Now that Meliodas is the Demon King, he cannot remain on earth. Though his friends acknowledge his fate, they are unable to accept it.

15. Fated Brothers

25m

Merlin rescues Elizabeth, who barely evades a falling boulder on her way to the Demon Realm with Meliodas. The Sins realize the Demon King is alive.

16. The Final Battle

25m

Elizabeth and Meliodas face the Demon King, who now possesses the body of Zeldris. Meanwhile, the Sins clash with a beast summoned by the Demon King.

17. The Voice Calling Your Name

25m

With Escanor's aid, Meliodas and Gowther reach the spirit world, where they aim to split the Demon King and Zeldris back into their own bodies.

18. The King Sings Alone

25m

Diane destroys the source of the Demon King's magic. Meanwhile, Escanor continues fighting the Demon King at full power, exceeding his limits.

19. The Struggle

25m

Escanor converts all of his life energy into magic to defeat the Demon King. Meliodas pleads with his comrade to stop, but Escanor refuses to listen.

20. Mortal Enemies

25m

Zeldris and the Sins corner the Demon King in both realms, but the King separates from his son’s body and possesses Britannia itself as his new vessel.

21. What the Witch Had Always Wanted

25m

The long-fought Holy War comes to a dramatic end. Peace returns to the Kingdom of Britannia once again, but a new threat looms on the horizon.

22. A Taste of Chaos

25m

The Sins are shocked by Merlin's longtime deception. Meanwhile, Merlin declares that Arthur has been recognized as the King of Chaos.

23. An Everlasting Kingdom

25m

A vicious beast in his true form, Cath attacks the reawakened Arthur. Now separated from the Sins, Merlin attempts to take on the monster herself.

24. Heirs

25m

Arthur’s battle with Cath comes to an epic conclusion. The Seven Deadly Sins go their separate ways as peace returns to the world once again.
